FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_info mi
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  6 AND t.production_year  <  2005 AND ci.person_id  >  2569964 AND ci.role_id  >  1
